00:32:04.732 --> 00:32:07.744
(Wuwei, Gansu, Pag-bid sa Proyekto ng 100 MW PV Power)
Pagkatapos ng isang bukas, patas, at walang kinikilingang

00:32:07.744 --> 00:32:08.704
proseso ng pag-bid

00:32:09.071 --> 00:32:11.291
at ng komite ng pagsusuri ng eksperto

00:32:11.452 --> 00:32:12.172
mahigpit na pagsusuri,

00:32:12.452 --> 00:32:13.831
sa huli ay napagpasyahan na natin

00:32:14.551 --> 00:32:16.591
na ang nanalong bidder para sa 100 MW

00:32:16.751 --> 00:32:18.071
proyektong photovoltaic power

00:32:18.071 --> 00:32:18.972
sa Wuwei, Gansu, ay

00:32:19.212 --> 00:32:20.511
Suzhou Shuangyuan

00:32:20.672 --> 00:32:22.271
Teknolohiyang Photovoltaic Co., Ltd.

00:32:22.611 --> 00:32:23.192
Shuangyuan!

00:32:26.732 --> 00:32:27.311
Magaling!

00:32:28.576 --> 00:32:29.856
(Seremoniya ng Pagpapalit ng Pangalan at Pagbubunyag ng Guang Yu sa Suzhou)
Maligayang Pagdating,

00:32:29.856 --> 00:32:31.392
(Photovoltaic Technology Co., Ltd.)
mga natatanging panauhin,

00:32:31.744 --> 00:32:33.216
para sa pagdalo sa aming kompanya

00:32:33.216 --> 00:32:34.912
pagpapalit ng pangalan at seremonya ng paglalahad ng plake.

00:32:35.372 --> 00:32:36.291
Sa isang mahirap na panahon,

00:32:36.791 --> 00:32:38.232
lahat ng tao sa aming kompanya

00:32:38.392 --> 00:32:40.172
nagpakita ng walang humpay na pagtitiyaga.

00:32:40.531 --> 00:32:42.872
Sa huli, nakamit natin
ang isang malaking tagumpay

00:32:43.031 --> 00:32:44.232
sa teknolohiya ng PV cell,

00:32:44.551 --> 00:32:46.452
nakakuha ng ilang mahahalagang order,

00:32:46.712 --> 00:32:48.111
at nakabangon mula sa aming pinagdadaanan.

00:32:48.732 --> 00:32:49.672
Sa masayang pagkakataong ito,

00:32:50.192 --> 00:32:52.172
opisyal nang pinalitan ng pangalan ang kompanya

00:32:52.591 --> 00:32:53.692
bilang Guang Yu Photovoltaic.

00:32:54.472 --> 00:32:55.492
Gamit ang 'Yu' bilang aming base,

00:32:55.732 --> 00:32:57.172
at 'Guang' bilang aming mapagkukunan,

00:32:58.111 --> 00:32:59.192
magkapit-bisig tayo

00:32:59.831 --> 00:33:00.712
at sumulong.

00:33:01.071 --> 00:33:01.732
Magaling!

00:33:04.632 --> 00:33:05.432
Salubungin natin

00:33:05.591 --> 00:33:06.771
Mr. Sheng Xianmin,

00:33:07.328 --> 00:33:08.736
Tagapangulo ng Sheng Yuan Group,

00:33:08.736 --> 00:33:10.492
at si Gng. Jiang Yun,

00:33:10.492 --> 00:33:11.892
Tagapangulo ng Yun Shang Investment,

00:33:11.932 --> 00:33:14.251
upang ilantad ang plake
para sa Guang Yu Photovoltaic.

00:33:18.152 --> 00:33:18.732
Lima.

00:33:20.091 --> 00:33:20.611
Apat.

00:33:21.791 --> 00:33:22.392
Tatlo.

00:33:23.472 --> 00:33:24.031
Dalawa.

00:33:24.751 --> 00:33:25.372
Isa.

00:33:25.751 --> 00:33:26.452
Ilabas ang belo!

00:33:27.031 --> 00:33:30.331
(Guang Yu Photovoltaic Technology Co., Ltd.)
Magaling!

00:33:52.500 --> 00:33:56.320
(Guang Yu Photovoltaic
Technology Co., Ltd.)

00:34:10.332 --> 00:34:12.412
Ang malaking entablado ay para sa mga malalaking boss.

00:34:12.912 --> 00:34:14.412
Pagbubunyag ng plake ng maliit na hardin

00:34:14.551 --> 00:34:15.071
ay para sa atin.

00:34:16.372 --> 00:34:17.492
Ginoong Lin, pakibuksan po ang takip.

00:34:19.552 --> 00:34:20.231
Hindi magkasama?

00:34:20.671 --> 00:34:21.412
Tinakpan ko ito.

00:34:21.504 --> 00:34:22.912
Siyempre dapat mo itong ibunyag.

00:34:22.912 --> 00:34:24.352
Kakaiba itong takpan at ilantad.

00:34:25.832 --> 00:34:26.772
Nahuhumaling sa seremonya?

00:34:28.640 --> 00:34:29.856
Pagkatapos ay gagawin mo ang countdown.

00:34:31.492 --> 00:34:33.292
Sabi ng isa na nahuhumaling sa seremonya.

00:34:37.651 --> 00:34:38.151
Lima.

00:34:38.892 --> 00:34:39.392
Apat.

00:34:40.071 --> 00:34:40.571
Tatlo.

00:34:41.892 --> 00:34:42.392
Dalawa.

00:34:43.611 --> 00:34:44.131
Isa.

00:34:49.364 --> 00:34:52.628
(Kagubatan ng Liu Guang)

00:34:58.707 --> 00:35:01.814
♪Hindi ko pa naramdaman ito dati♪

00:35:03.028 --> 00:35:05.632
♪Oh mananatili ba itong pareho♪

00:35:06.452 --> 00:35:08.448
♪Kahit na magbago ang mga panahon♪

00:35:08.448 --> 00:35:10.956
♪At ang buhay ay humahadlang♪

00:35:13.332 --> 00:35:14.671
Kailan mo palihim na binago ang pangalan nito?

00:35:15.912 --> 00:35:18.752
Noong naisip ko
ang pag-alis mo sa Shuangyuan,

00:35:19.511 --> 00:35:20.191
at hindi namin gagawin

00:35:20.332 --> 00:35:21.432
gugugol ng 10 oras pa

00:35:21.611 --> 00:35:22.671
magkasama araw-araw.

00:35:24.916 --> 00:35:27.616
♪Mahahanap natin ang daan pabalik sa kung kailan♪

00:35:28.275 --> 00:35:34.976
♪Sa lahat ng mga panahong ating
pinagdaanan at natutunan na tayo ay para sa isa't isa♪

00:35:36.972 --> 00:35:38.111
Kung patuloy kang magsasalita,

00:35:39.812 --> 00:35:41.211
Mawawalan ako ng determinasyon

00:35:41.912 --> 00:35:42.912
at ayokong umalis.

00:35:43.932 --> 00:35:46.412
Hinding-hindi, Dr. Lin.

00:35:47.531 --> 00:35:49.492
